We create art, music, literature – futile attempts to stave off the inevitability of oblivion.
We believe, against all evidence to the contrary, that there must be more to life than the mere consumption of time.
We form fragile bonds with one another, seeking comfort in the face of this existential despair.
Hope that there may be more to this existence than the dull thrum of entropy.
